- Always verify file path contains Left/LEFT before updating
- Preserve all other profile information unchanged
- Update status immediately when Left folder is detected
- Log all status updates to department log files
- Case-sensitive for "LEFT" status value (must be uppercase)
- Case-insensitive for folder name detection (Left/LEFT/left all match)
